The CommonTrust Network

URL = https://www.commontrustnetwork.org/?

"is a global registry of organizations that issue verifiable health credentials (such as SMART Health Cards). These organizations (called “Issuers” or “Health Data Sources”) are committed to empowering individuals with digital access to their health data using open, interoperable, and verifiable standards."

